{"tid":322510,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返工 成日比人覺得好唔認真","createTime":"2017-07-15T01:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T12:25:20.000Z","uid":26741,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cf7fe614305fe6a0ad89f52fb945c1a547587d","tid":322510,"uid":26741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:03:09.000Z","msg":"明明已經好認真做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇一睇電話就話我成日掛住玩 好hea<br />\n你地自己成日上ig fb 玩game 就係好勤力<br />\n仲話要睇住我做 驚我偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都未睇過我做嘅嘢就妄下判斷<br />\n真係心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我平時講嘢好搞笑 咁係咪應該變到唔講嘢咁佢先覺得我認真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f3c62004ac1b03e09f37a25c4625a69ee81dc3","tid":322510,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:04:30.000Z","msg":"可能做野個陣改一改講野個tone 唔好咁輕挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7873ecffebefc0a8be186384bee2908d652686","tid":322510,"uid":37922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f4a05b4be808f8713d34899cf97e47fd8529ff9","tid":322510,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"打份工都要顧咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cee726d1579d2883d7eb82fd3655a555c3ccd2","tid":322510,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係<br />\n第一日返工未有野做所以搞笑d輕鬆d<br />\n成team都因為咁熟絡左<br />\n但自此d同事就唔想同我合作做野<br />\n覺得我9fingfing唔認真<br />\n個個都係合作過一次先慢慢改觀<br />\n<br />\n依家轉左工 唔咁多嘴玩玩下<br />\n就變左大毒撚 無人理 融入唔到<br />\n一樣係唔比野我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奴性重到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji